Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia! We came\Nas fast as we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to wield the Elements\Nof Harmony once again and stop Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elements! They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony has to play\Nor the game is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our friendship... over?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who were you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony! Nopony whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie! Are we glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY? Need a good laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening to my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we might be due\Nfor a big old storm of chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are YOU laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You ponies are just\Nthe most fun I've had in aeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, QUIT IT!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You better think\Nbefore you laugh at the Pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...kie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,QUIT IT!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Ha ha ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This here diamond o' yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight said we should split it\Nsix way, since we uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:01:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...found it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it, punk. He's mine. All mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls, why are you\Nall acting like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to stick together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just too entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Discord!\NYou're not playing fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not playing fair?\NPerhaps we haven't met.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Discord. Spirit of chaos\Nand disharmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hellooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to find\Nthe Elements of Harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...when you took away the labyrinth\Nbefore we could get to the end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait! Did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought the Elements\Nwere *in* the labyrinth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Twists and turns are my master plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...then find the Elements\Nback where you began.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said they\Nwere in the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep trying, Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,♥ Maybe the magic of friendship ♥\Ncan help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll excuse me,\NI have some chaos to wreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate milk?! I hate chocolate milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Think, Twilight, think!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Find the Elements\Nback where you began...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Back where you began...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch my gem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm touching your gem, Rarity. Ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's you laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I just wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Home! Back where you began!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elements must be in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls! I'm certain this is\Nwhat Discord's riddle really meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get back to the library...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...I have a book that I just know\Ncan give us a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy, Angel! Mama's so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Weeell, I can see so much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord's turned our\Ndirt roads into soap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the new and improved Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are only my first changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This may look like fun, but it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture it, the chaos\Ncapital of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't picture anything.\NIt's too dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, wait a few minutes and you'll\Nsee it in the beautiful light of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville the chaos\Ncapital of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if I have anything to say about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:05:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're here. Everyone please\Nplease please just go inside, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,With pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate libraries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleeease, we gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, Twilight.\NI know what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The second I go in you'll have your\Nlittle minion Spike come and take Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tom?\N-Well, it's not going to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going in\Nwithout him, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do that for, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause you just look so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll ruin his beautiful finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for the love of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's everybody look so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask. I need you\Nto help me find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Twilight? What's\Nsoaking wet and clueless?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, I've had just about enou...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened to everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you just bring up\Nthe worst in us, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No time to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to find the reference guide\Nto Elements of Harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...before somepony does\Nsomething she'll regret!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elements of Harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I know exactly where that book is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy... You better\Ngive me that book!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack! Give me that book!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any book.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Do you even know\Nwhat you just stole?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but if you want it, I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,GIVE ME THAT BOOK!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she? Where is Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back! All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my book! AND I'M GONNA READ IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elements!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elements!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They were here all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you guys can defeat Discord\Nand put everything back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See, girls? We did it! We've found\Nthe Elements of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even care, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought it would\Nhappen. My friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...have turned into complete jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Necklace... Necklace...\NNecklace... Necklace...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...big crown-thingy.\NCome on, everypony! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Twilight.\NAren't you missing somepony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. We've got the liar, the grump,\Nthe hoarded and the brute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That just about covers it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Spike. You're\Nthe new Rainbow Dash. Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,B-b-but... what if she finds out\NI've been impersonating her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad. You're Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go defeat Discord so we don't\Never have to talk to each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,YEAH! WOOHOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out! Here comes Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well. I see you've\Nfound the Elements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord! I've figured out\Nyour lame riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in for it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly am. You've\Nclearly outduelled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it's time to meet my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to be\Ndefeated now, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire when ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Formation! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's workin'. There must be\Nsomethin' wrong with yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate the Elements of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,MINE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Twilight. I guess I better get\Nback upstairs and clean up the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with all this... whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. Sorry, Rainbow Crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo, ponies! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Harmony in Equestria\Nis officially dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord rules, Celestia drools.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault it didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Any of you! All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I better go too. I got new, better\Nfriends waitin' for me at the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm sick of you losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! Leave! See if I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need you guys either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With friends like you, who needs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you've got to\Nsee what I just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's priceless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, Twilight Sparkle. You've\Ngot to get into the spirit of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this is your new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pack your things, Spike. We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't ask where we're going,\N'cause... I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't... move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess...\Nhas been sending these...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...since I came back upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all the letters\NI've written to the Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...since I've lived in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would she send them back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Real friends don't care\Nwhat your cover is..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Friendship is a wondrous\Nand powerful thing..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"And like the path cut through the orchard,\Nthere'll be always a way through."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"The best thing to do is\Nto stay true to yourself..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"...special magical connection\Nwith her friends..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"...maybe even before she's met them."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! Spike, it's all so clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see? Discord's trying to\Ndistract us from what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows how powerful\Nour friendships are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he's trying to\Nkeep us from seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what I said\Nthe first day we arrived in Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that the future of Equestria\Ndidn't rest on me making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But the opposite is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The friendships I've made\Nsince I've been here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...would save Equestria\Nfrom Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they need to\Nsave it from Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to fight for my friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For them. For me. For Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just stay here and rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the whole fighting\Nfor friendship thing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I tried to defeat Discord...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...but none of my so-called friends\Nwould lift a hoof to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack! I'm here to fight\Nfor our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Now you wanna fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you when\NI was battlin' Discord?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a vision of us\Nfeudin' and fightin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't face the truth\Nso I started tellin' lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you ever forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Applejack!\NI just had the worst dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?\NGet away from my gem! Get Away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us never speak of this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I... I turned gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Rainbow Dash\Nwe can't use the Elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She could be anywhere by now.\NWe're never gonna find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we will. Cause she's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been looking everywhere for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord's still on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you to help us defeat him\Nwith your element: loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Loyalty-schmoyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you guys seen Ponyville?\NIt's a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying here in Cloudsdale\Nwhere everything is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How in Equestria could she think that\Ntiny patch of clouds is Cloudsdale?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The same way he got you to think that\Ncheap rock was a bona fide diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we agreed\Nnever to speak of it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You grab Rainbow Dash\Nand hold her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack will lower me\Ndown from this rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I can cast\Nthe memory spell on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm just wondering\Nif it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...if I hold you down\Nagainst your will for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice try. Ponyville's\Nyour problem, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Fluttershy!\NWe've gotta catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:16:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,PinkiIEEE! You were supposed\Nto secure the roOOPE!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity! Pinkie! Hold on!\NY'all are slowin' 'er down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Fluttershy. Would you\Nbe a dear and FLY FASTER, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't catch her, Discord wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That... big... dumb... MEANIE!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Applejack! Last rope!\NMake it count!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme go! I don't need you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Ponyville?!\NWhere are the Elements?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we stop Discord?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a little early\Nfor a group hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chaos is a wonderful, wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...as friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You couldn't break apart\Nour friendship for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Applejack. Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who made you a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you ever learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what\Nwe've learned, Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've learned that\Nfriendship isn't always easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...but there's no doubt\Nit's worth fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, gag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Go ahead.\NTry and use your little Elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Friend me". Just make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm missing some excellent chaos here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, ladies! Let's show him\Nwhat friendship can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nooo!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We are gathered here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...to once again honor\Nthe heroism of these six friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...who stood up\Nto the villain Discord...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...and saved Equestria\Nfrom eternal chaos.
